<br>
The only part we can really active work on is Balic's quest at the moment. If you want results, step ahead and make a chart of combinations, and let us know your results. I have done a part of this and I have got a result, even if its not a positive one: none of the magician research words and wizard research runes yield a valid combination.<br>
<br>
This is what has to be tested:<br>
- Necro research words and wizard research runes.<br>
- Enc research words and wizard research runes.<br>
<br>
The bad thing is each of these have very large numbers of possible combinations (you can limit this somewhat if you use the hint of Balic, words and runes of similar power, but this may lead to missing a combine). But if noone does step ahead and makes a chart for these, we wont get any further (yes I know, people have tried many combinations but there are probably a lot still missing, and without a full chart we cant argue anything).<br>
<br>
Remember that negative results can help too. If we knew that no wizard runes and enc/nec words yield a valid combine we would be a huge step further.<br>
